#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.21:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.21:0.2"
msgid "3. Gahapativagga"
msgstr "3. Householders"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 21. Paṭhamauggasutta → vesālikauggasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Paṭhamauggasutta"
msgstr "21. With Ugga of Vesālī (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.209"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Vesālī, at the Great Wood, in the "
"hall with the peaked roof."

msgctxt "an8.21:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

#. VAR: abbhutehi dhammehi → abbhutadhammehi (s1-3, mr)
msgctxt "an8.21:1.3"
msgid ""
"“aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgataṃ uggaṃ "
"gahapatiṃ vesālikaṃ dhārethā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, you should remember the householder Ugga of Vesālī as someone "
"who has eight amazing and incredible qualities.”"

msgctxt "an8.21:1.4"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "an8.21:1.5"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ pāvisi."
msgstr ""
"When he had spoken, the Holy One got up from his seat and entered his "
"dwelling."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena "
"uggassa gahapatino vesālikassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"paññatte āsane nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then a certain mendicant robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and "
"robe, went to the home of the householder Ugga of Vesālī, where he sat on "
"the seat spread out."

msgctxt "an8.21:2.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho uggo gahapati vesāliko yena so bhikkhu tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"taṃ bhikkhuṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho uggaṃ "
"gahapatiṃ vesālikaṃ so bhikkhu etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Ugga of Vesālī went up to that mendicant, bowed, and sat down to one "
"side. The mendicant said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhahi kho tvaṃ, gahapati, acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgato "
"bhagavatā byākato."
msgstr ""
"“Householder, the Buddha declared that you have eight amazing and incredible "
"qualities."

msgctxt "an8.21:3.2"
msgid ""
"Katame te, gahapati, aṭṭha acchariyā abbhutā dhammā, yehi tvaṃ samannāgato "
"bhagavatā byākato”ti?"
msgstr "What are the eight qualities that he spoke of?”"

msgctxt "an8.21:3.3"
msgid "“Na kho ahaṃ, bhante, jānāmi:"
msgstr "“Sir, I don’t know"

msgctxt "an8.21:3.4"
msgid ""
"‘katamehi aṭṭhahi acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgato bhagavatā "
"byākato’ti."
msgstr ""
"what eight amazing and incredible qualities the Buddha was referring to."

msgctxt "an8.21:3.5"
msgid "Api ca, bhante, ye me aṭṭha acchariyā abbhutā dhammā saṃvijjanti,;"
msgstr "But these eight amazing and incredible qualities are found in me."

msgctxt "an8.21:3.6"
msgid "taṃ suṇohi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "an8.21:3.7"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, gahapatī”ti kho so bhikkhu uggassa gahapatino vesālikassa paccassosi."
msgstr "“Yes, householder,” replied the mendicant."

msgctxt "an8.21:3.8"
msgid "Uggo gahapati vesāliko etadavoca:"
msgstr "Ugga of Vesālī said this:"

msgctxt "an8.21:3.9"
msgid "“yadāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavantaṃ paṭhamaṃ dūratova addasaṃ;"
msgstr "“Sir, when I first saw the Buddha off in the distance,"

msgctxt "an8.21:3.10"
msgid "saha dassaneneva me, bhante, bhagavato cittaṃ pasīdi."
msgstr "my heart was inspired as soon as I saw him."

msgctxt "an8.21:3.11"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, bhante, paṭhamo acchariyo abbhuto dhammo saṃvijjati. (1)"
msgstr "This is the first incredible and amazing quality found in me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.210"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:4.1"
msgid "So kho ahaṃ, bhante, pasannacitto bhagavantaṃ payirupāsiṃ."
msgstr "With confident heart I paid homage to the Buddha."

msgctxt "an8.21:4.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa me bhagavā anupubbiṃ kathaṃ kathesi, seyyathidaṃ—dānakathaṃ sīlakathaṃ "
"saggakathaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"The Buddha taught me step by step, with a talk on giving, ethical conduct, "
"and heaven."

msgctxt "an8.21:4.3"
msgid "kāmānaṃ ādīnavaṃ okāraṃ saṅkilesaṃ, nekkhamme ānisaṃsaṃ pakāsesi."
msgstr ""
"He explained the drawbacks of sensual pleasures, so sordid and corrupt, and "
"the benefit of renunciation."

msgctxt "an8.21:4.4"
msgid ""
"Yadā maṃ bhagavā aññāsi kallacittaṃ muducittaṃ vinīvaraṇacittaṃ udaggacittaṃ "
"pasannacittaṃ, atha yā buddhānaṃ sāmukkaṃsikā dhammadesanā taṃ pakāsesi—"
msgstr ""
"And when he knew that my mind was ready, pliable, rid of hindrances, joyful, "
"and confident he explained the special teaching of the Buddhas:"

msgctxt "an8.21:4.5"
msgid "dukkhaṃ, samudayaṃ, nirodhaṃ, maggaṃ."
msgstr "suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path."

msgctxt "an8.21:4.6"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi nāma suddhaṃ vatthaṃ apagatakāḷakaṃ sammadeva rajanaṃ "
"paṭiggaṇheyya;"
msgstr "Just as a clean cloth rid of stains would properly absorb dye,"

msgctxt "an8.21:4.7"
msgid ""
"evamevaṃ kho me tasmiṃyeva āsane virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi:"
msgstr ""
"in that very seat the stainless, immaculate vision of the Dhamma arose in me:"

msgctxt "an8.21:4.8"
msgid "‘yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman’ti."
msgstr "‘Everything that has a beginning has an end.’"

msgctxt "an8.21:4.9"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, bhante, diṭṭhadhammo pattadhammo viditadhammo pariyogāḷhadhammo "
"tiṇṇavicikiccho vigatakathaṅkatho vesārajjappatto aparappaccayo satthusāsane "
msgstr ""
"I saw, attained, understood, and fathomed the Dhamma. I went beyond doubt, "
"got rid of indecision, and became self-assured and independent of others "
"regarding the Teacher’s instructions. "

msgctxt "an8.21:4.10"
msgid ""
"tattheva buddhañca dhammañca saṅghañca saraṇaṃ agamāsiṃ, "
"brahmacariyapañcamāni ca sikkhāpadāni samādiyiṃ."
msgstr ""
"Right there I went for refuge to the Buddha, his teaching, and the Saṅgha. "
"And I undertook the five training rules with chastity as the fifth."

msgctxt "an8.21:4.11"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, bhante, dutiyo acchariyo abbhuto dhammo saṃvijjati. (2)"
msgstr "This is the second incredible and amazing quality found in me."

# Rendering komariya as teenage following the sikkhama who is attharasavassa kumaribhuta. The ideal age for marriage was considered sixteen. “Girls” is too young, while a “young wife” seems more like early twenties.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:5.1"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, catasso komāriyo pajāpatiyo ahesuṃ."
msgstr "I had four teenage wives."

msgctxt "an8.21:5.2"
msgid ""
"Atha khvāhaṃ, bhante, yena tā pajāpatiyo tenupasaṅkamiṃ; upasaṅkamitvā tā "
"pajāpatiyo etadavacaṃ:"
msgstr "And I went to them and said:"

#. VAR: samādinnāni → samādiṇṇāni (mr)
msgctxt "an8.21:5.3"
msgid "‘mayā kho, bhaginiyo, brahmacariyapañcamāni sikkhāpadāni samādinnāni."
msgstr ""
"‘Sisters, I’ve undertaken the five training rules with chastity as fifth."

msgctxt "an8.21:5.4"
msgid ""
"Yā icchati sā idheva bhoge ca bhuñjatu puññāni ca karotu, sakāni vā "
"ñātikulāni gacchatu."
msgstr ""
"If you wish, you may stay here, enjoy my wealth, and do good deeds. Or you "
"can return to your own families."

msgctxt "an8.21:5.5"
msgid "Hoti vā pana purisādhippāyo, kassa vo dammī’ti?"
msgstr "Or would you prefer if I gave you to another man?’"

msgctxt "an8.21:5.6"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, sā, bhante, jeṭṭhā pajāpati maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When I said this, my eldest wife said to me:"

msgctxt "an8.21:5.7"
msgid "‘itthannāmassa maṃ, ayyaputta, purisassa dehī’ti."
msgstr "‘My lord, please give me to such-and-such a man.’"

msgctxt "an8.21:5.8"
msgid ""
"Atha kho ahaṃ, bhante, taṃ purisaṃ pakkosāpetvā vāmena hatthena pajāpatiṃ "
"gahetvā dakkhiṇena hatthena bhiṅgāraṃ gahetvā tassa purisassa oṇojesiṃ."
msgstr ""
"Then I summoned that man. Taking my wife with my left hand and a ceremonial "
"vase with my right, I presented her to that man with the pouring of water."

msgctxt "an8.21:5.9"
msgid ""
"Komāriṃ kho panāhaṃ, bhante, dāraṃ pariccajanto nābhijānāmi cittassa "
"aññathattaṃ."
msgstr "But I can’t recall getting upset while giving away my teenage wife."

msgctxt "an8.21:5.10"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, bhante, tatiyo acchariyo abbhuto dhammo saṃvijjati. (3)"
msgstr "This is the third incredible and amazing quality found in me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.211"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:6.1"
msgid "Saṃvijjanti kho pana me, bhante, kule bhogā."
msgstr "And though my family has wealth,"

msgctxt "an8.21:6.2"
msgid "Te ca kho appaṭivibhattā sīlavantehi kalyāṇadhammehi."
msgstr "it’s shared without reserve with ethical people of good character."

msgctxt "an8.21:6.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, bhante, catuttho acchariyo abbhuto dhammo saṃvijjati. (4)"
msgstr "This is the fourth incredible and amazing quality found in me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:7.1"
msgid "Yaṃ kho panāhaṃ, bhante, bhikkhuṃ payirupāsāmi;"
msgstr "When I pay homage to a mendicant,"

msgctxt "an8.21:7.2"
msgid "sakkaccaṃyeva payirupāsāmi, no asakkaccaṃ."
msgstr "I do so carefully, not carelessly."

msgctxt "an8.21:7.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, bhante, pañcamo acchariyo abbhuto dhammo saṃvijjati. (5)"
msgstr "This is the fifth incredible and amazing quality found in me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:8.1"
msgid "So ce, bhante, me āyasmā dhammaṃ deseti;"
msgstr "If that venerable teaches me the Dhamma,"

msgctxt "an8.21:8.2"
msgid "sakkaccaṃyeva suṇomi, no asakkaccaṃ."
msgstr "I listen carefully, not carelessly."

msgctxt "an8.21:8.3"
msgid "No ce me so āyasmā dhammaṃ deseti, ahamassa dhammaṃ desemi."
msgstr "But if they don’t teach me the Dhamma, I teach them."

msgctxt "an8.21:8.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, bhante, chaṭṭho acchariyo abbhuto dhammo saṃvijjati. (6)"
msgstr "This is the sixth incredible and amazing quality found in me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:9.1"
msgid "Anacchariyaṃ kho pana maṃ, bhante, devatā upasaṅkamitvā ārocenti:"
msgstr "It’s not unusual for deities to come to me and announce:"

msgctxt "an8.21:9.2"
msgid "‘svākkhāto, gahapati, bhagavatā dhammo’ti."
msgstr "‘Householder, the Buddha’s teaching is well explained!’"

msgctxt "an8.21:9.3"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, bhante, tā devatā evaṃ vadāmi:"
msgstr "When they say this I say to them:"

msgctxt "an8.21:9.4"
msgid ""
"‘vadeyyātha vā evaṃ kho tumhe devatā no vā vadeyyātha, atha kho svākkhāto "
"bhagavatā dhammo’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The Buddha’s teaching is well explained, regardless of whether or not you "
"deities say so!’"

#. VAR: unnatiṃ → uṇṇatiṃ (bj, mr) | uṇṇanti (s1-3)
msgctxt "an8.21:9.5"
msgid "Na kho panāhaṃ, bhante, abhijānāmi tatonidānaṃ cittassa unnatiṃ:"
msgstr "But I don’t recall getting too excited by the fact that"

msgctxt "an8.21:9.6"
msgid "‘maṃ vā devatā upasaṅkamanti, ahaṃ vā devatāhi saddhiṃ sallapāmī’ti."
msgstr "the deities come to me, and I have a conversation with them."

msgctxt "an8.21:9.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, bhante, sattamo acchariyo abbhuto dhammo saṃvijjati. (7)"
msgstr "This is the seventh incredible and amazing quality found in me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:10.1"
msgid ""
"Yānimāni, bhante, bhagavatā desitāni pañcorambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni, nāhaṃ "
"tesaṃ kiñci attani appahīnaṃ samanupassāmi."
msgstr ""
"Of the five lower fetters taught by the Buddha, I don’t see any that I haven’"
"t given up."

msgctxt "an8.21:10.2"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho me, bhante, aṭṭhamo acchariyo abbhuto dhammo saṃvijjati. (8)"
msgstr "This is the eighth incredible and amazing quality found in me."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.212"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:11.1"
msgid "Ime kho me, bhante, aṭṭha acchariyā abbhutā dhammā saṃvijjanti."
msgstr "These eight amazing and incredible qualities are found in me."

msgctxt "an8.21:11.2"
msgid "Na ca kho ahaṃ jānāmi—"
msgstr "But I don’t know"

#. VAR: katamehi cāhaṃ → katamehipahaṃ (bj) | katamehi pāhaṃ (pts1) | katamehipāhaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an8.21:11.3"
msgid ""
"katamehi cāhaṃ aṭṭhahi acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgato bhagavatā "
"byākato”ti."
msgstr ""
"what eight amazing and incredible qualities the Buddha was referring to.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:12.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho so bhikkhu uggassa gahapatino vesālikassa nivesane piṇḍapātaṃ "
"gahetvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"Then that mendicant, after taking alms-food in Ugga of Vesālī’s home, got up "
"from his seat and left."

msgctxt "an8.21:12.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho so bhikkhu pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then after the meal, on his return from alms-round, he went to the Buddha, "
"bowed, and sat down to one side."

msgctxt "an8.21:12.3"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu yāvatako ahosi uggena gahapatinā vesālikena "
"saddhiṃ kathāsallāpo, taṃ sabbaṃ bhagavato ārocesi."
msgstr ""
"He informed the Buddha of all he had discussed with the householder Ugga of "
"Vesālī. The Buddha said:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an8.21:13.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhu."
msgstr "“Good, good, monk!"

msgctxt "an8.21:13.2"
msgid ""
"Yathā taṃ uggo gahapati vesāliko sammā byākaramāno byākareyya, imeheva kho, "
"bhikkhu, aṭṭhahi acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgato uggo gahapati "
"vesāliko mayā byākato."
msgstr ""
"When I declared that the householder Ugga of Vesālī was someone who has "
"eight amazing and incredible qualities, I was referring to the same eight "
"qualities that he rightly explained to you."

msgctxt "an8.21:13.3"
msgid ""
"Imehi ca pana, bhikkhu, aṭṭhahi acchariyehi abbhutehi dhammehi samannāgataṃ "
"uggaṃ gahapatiṃ vesālikaṃ dhārehī”ti."
msgstr ""
"You should remember the householder Ugga of Vesālī as someone who has these "
"eight amazing and incredible qualities.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.21:13.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
